BT /F1 10 Tf 54.0 612.7 Td (The final steering angle is:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 590.6 Td (delta_total_t = clip\(delta_action_t + delta_lane_bias_t\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.0 570.5 Td (The clipping cap is 16 deg up to 60 km/h and 0.35 deg above 60 km/h. Steering is smoothed) Tj ET
