BT /F2 14 Tf 54.0 530.4 Td (Bicycle Rollout) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.0 501.3 Td (The initial state is estimated from the past ego trajectory using Savitzky-Golay) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.0 488.3 Td (derivatives:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 466.2 Td (v0 = sqrt\(vx^2 + vy^2\)) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 455.2 Td (theta0 = atan2\(vy, vx\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.0 435.1 Td (Then KITE rolls forward for 25 steps:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 413.0 Td (dt = 0.2 s) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 402.0 Td (L = 2.7 m) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 391.0 Td () Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 380.0 Td (v_{t+1} = max\(0, v_t + a_t dt\)) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 369.0 Td (theta_{t+1} = theta_t + \(v_{t+1} / L\) tan\(delta_total_t\) dt) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 358.0 Td (x_{t+1} = x_t + v_{t+1} cos\(theta_{t+1}\) dt) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 68.0 347.0 Td (y_{t+1} = y_t + v_{t+1} sin\(theta_{t+1}\) dt) Tj ET
